lingua franca<br />\n<br />\n當佢地日常用咁多英文，英文好過我哋都好正常，應該話英文係佔咗佢哋社會入面一個好重要嘅部分<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">香港係一個好單一種族嘅社會</span>，我哋主要溝通嘅語言係廣東話，所以好少用到英文<br />\n<br />\n你嗰個比較其實唔valid</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港本來有圍頭、客家、水上等原居民，之後又有廣府、潮汕、上海、蘇浙人。<br />\n<br />\n每度人都有自己語言喎</blockquote><br />\n佢哋學廣東話做共同語言而唔係好似新加坡咁用英文<br />\n同埋老老柒柒，依家仲有幾多人母語係客家話/上海話？大部份都係一出世就學廣東話啦"},{"pid":"b7ff2553c913dde0fe4da1b3b96f96cc00301e8a","tid":189381,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"我朋友話佢外國讀u 雙degree都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ffb216a12c0bc313c799d5891e8b38b037f79d","tid":189381,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"睇套戲都只係想放鬆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要作賤自已<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0534a83d849e125be8f9f9142e20a55ece9bfd4f","tid":189381,"uid":10699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇套戲都只係想放鬆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要作賤自已<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇香港啲王晶電影算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61164449e087ba3b55fed54feaf61fca48f39bbf","tid":189381,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"點解冇其實唔難<br />\n<br />\n睇下係咩戲, 好多slang / technical terms 我就會開始亂, 連本身識嘅字都變咗聽唔到"},{"pid":"5023ceddbdd2e07d5d617e5b522d41840df675ea","tid":189381,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇套戲都只係想放鬆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要作賤自已<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /