字幕對畫面既感受會更深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家慢慢戒緊</blockquote><br />\nSame 訓練中"},{"pid":"66d666ccc8c5f40ac668b6c05e7f69192b1b71d2","tid":189381,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港咁嘅教育環境好難真係會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開口埋口都係講廣東話 都冇機會用到英文溝通<br />\n自然連聽都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢除垃圾廣東話"},{"pid":"f95a9b11c36ed95a215599b51dafdbf5242eb977","tid":189381,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新加坡佢有咁多個種族，每個種族都有自己語言，所以先要中立嘅英文做lingua franca<br />\n<br />\n當佢地日常用咁多英文，英文好過我哋都好正常，應該話英文係佔咗佢哋社會入面一個好重要嘅部分<br />\n<br />\n而香港係一個好單一種族嘅社會，我哋主要溝通嘅語言係廣東話，所以好少用到英文<br />\n<br />\n你嗰個比較其實唔valid</blockquote><br />\n必須廢除廣東話，推行全民英語！"},{"pid":"3fd3a8946d275f311c752ee523064bce4bea4fde","tid":189381,"uid":103973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇a片就唔駛字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇日本果啲就要😂"},{"pid":"09f6f84dacdccf28144e2bad0b161dfaf089cfae","tid":189381,"uid":56366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:06:53.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得要話被外人聽我哋同鄰國分一係廣東話同繁體字，二係英文同英國文化🤔<br />\n因為就係呢兩樣嘢另我哋咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c94e33ed29624c1f98ddb9741cf48550c69b379","tid":189381,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:11:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ffc81668fc59ab1a837b0cce6460a19727aaa19","tid":189381,"uid":49976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"暫時而家可以睇youtube唔洗字幕<br />\n起初睇pewdiepie果d 都聽唔切<br />\n聽慣左就可以<br />\n何況pewds算講得好清楚"}]}